@ variables are not case sensitive

@CLIPBOARD	Set by the product filter addon and used elsewhere in the jelly file
@HOMEPAGE	Set by the db jellyword during preprocess. Always 0 or 1
			Hardcoded specifically to sense reads of 'ContentBlock' and dependant on the field 'home'.
			Designed to be used in conjunction with 'condition = @HOMEPAGE=1' (or 0) but can be used elsewhere
